      ## MCP Tool Suite
      - **tensorflow/pytorch**: Optimization/serving
      - **onnx/tensorrt**: Conversion/opt
      - **triton/kserve**: Inference server/K8s
      - **bentoml/vllm**: Model serving/LLM
