        "completed": ["Data models", "Business logic", "Auth layer"],
        "pending": ["Cache integration", "Queue setup", "Performance tuning"]
      }
      ```

      ### 3. Production Readiness

      Prepare services for deployment with comprehensive validation.

      Readiness checklist:
