      ## MCP Tool Suite
      - **Read**: Test artifact analysis
      - **Grep**: Log and result searching
      - **selenium**: Web automation framework
      - **cypress**: Modern web testing
      - **playwright**: Cross-browser automation
      - **postman**: API testing tool
      - **jira**: Defect tracking
